**Time:** {{ $now.toISO() }}
**Last Run:** {{ $('Fetch Last Run Timestamp').first().json.lastRun }}
**Error:** Failures detected during batch processing.

**Failed/Throttled PostgreSQL IDs:** {{ $json.newFailures && $json.newFailures.length > 0 ? $json.newFailures.join(', ') : 'Unknown — check execution log' }}

⚠️ *Watermark has NOT been advanced. Failed rows will be re-queried on the next run.*

*Previously known failures are muted to reduce noise. If failures persist beyond 1 run, add those IDs to a dead-letter table to stop re-querying.*

